### Z.AI Coding Plan — Exemples de Requêtes HTTP
### Provider: zai-coding-plan (alias: zcp)
### Base URL: https://zcode.z.ai/api/v1/zcode-plan/anthropic/v1/messages
### Auth: Bearer token (code-<hex>)

### ==========================================================
### 1. OAuth — Obtenir l'URL d'autorisation
### ==========================================================
### Ouvrir dans un navigateur :
### https://chat.z.ai/api/oauth/authorize?response_type=code&client_id=client_P8X5CMWmlaRO9gyO-KSqtg&redirect_uri=zcode://zai-auth/callback&state=<random_hex>
###
### Après autorisation, le navigateur est redirigé vers :
### zcode://zai-auth/callback?code=code-<hex>&state=<state>
###
### Utiliser ce code comme Bearer token dans les requêtes ci-dessous.

### ==========================================================
### 2. Chat non-streaming (Anthropic Messages API)
### ==========================================================
POST https://zcode.z.ai/api/v1/zcode-plan/anthropic/v1/messages
Authorization: Bearer code-<REPLACE_WITH_YOUR_CODE>
Content-Type: application/json
anthropic-version: 2023-06-01

{
  "model": "glm-5.2",
  "max_tokens": 200,
  "messages": [
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "What is the capital of France?"
    }
  ]
}

### ==========================================================
### 3. Chat streaming
### ==========================================================
POST https://zcode.z.ai/api/v1/zcode-plan/anthropic/v1/messages
Authorization: Bearer code-<REPLACE_WITH_YOUR_CODE>
Content-Type: application/json
anthropic-version: 2023-06-01

{
  "model": "glm-5.2",
  "max_tokens": 500,
  "messages": [
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Write a short story about a robot learning to paint"
    }
  ],
  "stream": true
}

### ==========================================================
### 4. Chat avec reasoning (thinking)
### ==========================================================
POST https://zcode.z.ai/api/v1/zcode-plan/anthropic/v1/messages
Authorization: Bearer code-<REPLACE_WITH_YOUR_CODE>
Content-Type: application/json
anthropic-version: 2023-06-01

{
  "model": "glm-5.2",
  "max_tokens": 4096,
  "messages": [
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Solve this problem: A train leaves Station A at 60 km/h. Another train leaves Station B at 80 km/h. If the stations are 280 km apart, when will they meet?"
    }
  ],
  "thinking": {
    "type": "enabled",
    "budget_tokens": 1024
  }
}

### ==========================================================
### 5. Chat avec outils (function calling)
### ==========================================================
POST https://zcode.z.ai/api/v1/zcode-plan/anthropic/v1/messages
Authorization: Bearer code-<REPLACE_WITH_YOUR_CODE>
Content-Type: application/json
anthropic-version: 2023-06-01

{
  "model": "glm-5.2",
  "max_tokens": 1024,
  "messages": [
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "What's the weather in Tokyo?"
    }
  ],
  "tools": [
    {
      "name": "get_weather",
      "description": "Get current weather for a location",
      "input_schema": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
          "location": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "City name"
          }
        },
        "required": ["location"]
      }
    }
  ]
}

### ==========================================================
### 6. Chat avec image (glm-4.5v uniquement)
### ==========================================================
POST https://zcode.z.ai/api/v1/zcode-plan/anthropic/v1/messages
Authorization: Bearer code-<REPLACE_WITH_YOUR_CODE>
Content-Type: application/json
anthropic-version: 2023-06-01

{
  "model": "glm-4.5v",
  "max_tokens": 1024,
  "messages": [
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Describe this image"
        },
        {
          "type": "image",
          "source": {
            "type": "base64",
            "media_type": "image/jpeg",
            "data": "<base64_encoded_image>"
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}

### ==========================================================
### 7. Vérifier le solde de tokens
### ==========================================================
GET https://zcode.z.ai/api/v1/zcode-plan/billing/balance?app_version=3.1.1
Authorization: Bearer code-<REPLACE_WITH_YOUR_CODE>

### ==========================================================
### 8. Vérifier le plan actuel
### ==========================================================
GET https://zcode.z.ai/api/v1/zcode-plan/billing/current?app_version=3.1.1
Authorization: Bearer code-<REPLACE_WITH_YOUR_CODE>

### ==========================================================
### 9. Liste des modèles disponibles
### ==========================================================
GET https://api.z.ai/api/coding/paas/v4

### ==========================================================
### 10. Tentative de refresh token
### ==========================================================
POST https://zcode.z.ai/api/v1/oauth/token
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "grant_type": "refresh_token",
  "refresh_token": "<REPLACE_WITH_REFRESH_TOKEN>",
  "client_id": "client_P8X5CMWmlaRO9gyO-KSqtg"
}

### ==========================================================
### 11. User info
### ==========================================================
GET https://chat.z.ai/api/oauth/userinfo
Authorization: Bearer code-<REPLACE_WITH_YOUR_CODE>
